                    </div>
                    <span>This is one book that I highly recommend if you are looking for truth and a way for all of humanity to come together in peace. It is a compelling read, and one that sets a true example of the higher road to follow for us all. </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A Breath Of Hope</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>16</span>
                      /
                      <span>16</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2004-05-26</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>I believe what Jimmy Carter wrote on the inside cover, "that this book could change history."   Remember the first picture of the earth from space?  This book is a visionary view of the earth from the heart of a truly heroic insightful soul.  Do not let the number of the pages fool you into thinking it is a quick read...it is rather to be savored and pondered.  You will want to read it out loud to be sure others hear these words.  <br>  This writing brings perspective in a world that currently seems off center.  Balance is what we need most as humankind faces all the days ahead.  It will make you smile, laugh, sigh and perhaps cry, but you will be the richer for it all.</span>
                  
              
